{"tid":1100970,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【掛勾】若失歐聯席位 曼聯球員全部減薪四成","createTime":"2019-04-10T18:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T07:56:26.000Z","uid":173952,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f187f5f530ae809e010cb95e19d619e2faf100af","tid":1100970,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T18:28:11.000Z","msg":"歐聯席位對於球隊有多重要？除了可以吸引其他球員轉會外，同時影響球隊的收入，有外國傳媒報道，如果曼聯失去下季歐聯席位，全部球員都需要減薪 25% ，無一倖免。<br />\n根據外國傳媒報道，曼聯所有球員的合約條款中，都列明薪酬與球隊成績掛勾，如果球隊無法進入歐聯，下一季的薪酬將會自動調整，減薪 25% ，除此之外，根據曼聯與贊助商 Adidas 簽訂的合同，如果球隊連續兩季無緣歐聯，相關贊助金額都會下調三成。<br />\n事實上，有關條款並不是甚麼新鮮事，兩年前普巴帶領曼聯重返歐聯後，周薪馬上增至 30 萬鎊，可見如果曼聯如果錯失歐聯席位，陣中主動難免會想離隊他投。"},{"pid":"f7431a4ecf0a7633545c8cc28ef799788ff1c511","tid":1100970,"uid":12680,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T18:53:02.000Z","msg":"咁而家做緊義工既山神咪要倒貼比曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大慈善家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f26c88697f83ed66bc9ed07722160fa0ef06dc","tid":1100970,"uid":371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f7431a4ecf0a7633545c8cc28ef799788ff1c511","tid":1100970,"uid":12680,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T18:53:02.000Z","msg":"咁而家做緊義工既山神咪要倒貼比曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大慈善家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T18:57:40.000Z","msg":"0減四成都係0啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未使倒貼住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3bd1d0cd06d712c9ad4f64318c182c1c6aae78d","tid":1100970,"uid":165817,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T19:13:58.000Z","msg":"25%係四分一 同四成爭好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50bbe3523e89a28b59b1974d2286a9b39fb8a40f","tid":1100970,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score